<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">用左手使用滑鼠</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">如果您是左撇子，可以把滑鼠/觸控板左右鍵的行為交換，使用起來會比較舒服。</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">點擊<span class="gui">選單列</span>最右邊的圖示，選擇<span class="gui">系統設定值</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Open <span class="gui">Mouse &amp; Touchpad</span>.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">In the <span class="gui">General</span> section, switch <span class="gui">Primary button</span>
  to <span class="gui">Right</span>.</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<div class="note" title="備註"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">這個設定值將會影響您的滑鼠與觸控板，加上其他指向裝置。</p></div></div></div></div>
</div>
